title.rendered: BOSS AIR 4 VALVE AIR SUSPENSION BLOCK

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR 4 VALVE AIR SUSPENSION BLOCK

Boss Air 4 Valve Air Suspension Block available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

The new Boss Dual application direct acting pneumatic control valve for airbag suspension features:

  • 1/4″ NPT ports
  • Extra compact size
  • Sealant less threads when using Boss Air’s optional fittings kit for an air tight seal

Extra options available include:

  • Gauge Kit
    • Dual needle gauge 200psi with fittings and 10mtrs of Airline
  • 1/4″ Airline Fittings Kit
    • 1/4″ Airline valve fitting kit sealant-less
  • Remote Nitto Add-on
    • Add a remote Nitto Coupling so you can “plug-in” to pump up tyres or use air tools
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
